.DT
flower
$MUDNAME$ Player Help
flower

.SH Name
.SI 5
flowers - a barrel of happiness or sorrow for people
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
braid hair of <living> with <object>
braid <living> hair with <object>
braid <object> in <living> hair
unbraid <flower(s)> from my hair
remove <flower(s)> from my hair
attach <flower(s)> to <clothing>
remove <flower(s)> from <object>
unattach <flower(s)> from <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
In addition to purely aesthetic value, flowers can also be braided
into the hair of another or yourself.  They can later be unbraided
should the recipient grow tired of having any amongst their locks.

Is is also possible to attach flowers to clothing items for
additional viewing pleasure.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> braid hair of isilwen with purple rose
> braid isilwen hair with purple rose
> braid purple rose in isilwen hair
> unbraid roses from my hair
> remove withered roses from my hair
> attach purple roses to black dress
> remove purple roses from black dress
> unattach purple roses from black dress
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5

.EP
